Job Description
We need a sales person capable of marketing our products to the clients and get orders from them. We are a website development company and we need a person who is really capable of visiting industries and people to get orders from them regarding Website Development, SEO Services, IP Cameras installation and who can also keep following people to get services from us.Candidate should be capable of performing multiple tasks and should be trustworthy as it will also include financial transactions so honest person is required.
Job Specification
Candidate should be capable of following:- English Language (Atleast have know how)- Professional Attitude- Well Personality- Capable of closing dealsFollowing incentives will be given:- 5% Commission on every deal closed- Fuel Allowance- Bike Maintenance AllowanceCandidate should must have his own bike. We need a pro of this field not a newbie.Thanks
